headline: Northeast Mississippi Community College Becomes First School to Deploy Mobile Credential on Transact IDX® Platform
summary: SCOTTSDALE, Ariz., October 01, 2025--Transact + CBORD leads the market in offering mobile credential solutions to community colleges, expanding student services beyond large universities.
